Integrated marketing communication. Customer behaviour. Business relationship management. Customer relationship management.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to provide knowledge and practical skills about marketing communication and its organization.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon the completion of the course the student: 1) understands the nature and principles of (integrated) marketing communication and be able to apply them;  2) understands the importance and role of business relationships in marketing communication and be able to maintain and establish useful business relationships;  3) understands the basic principles of customer behaviour and be able to take them into account when planning marketing communication.
